<h2 class="centered padded-title">Why joining us?</h2>

<div class="arguments-container">
  <div class="arguments col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6">
    <div class="argument-box card-1" style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'oneclick.png', crop: :fill; %>') ;">
      <dl>
        <dt><h4 class="centered why-title">Import your LinkedIn Profile</h4></dt>
        <dd>Complete your profile in only a few seconds by importing all your data directly from LinkedIn. The time you had to spend fifteen minutes on a jobboard to complete your profile is over. One click, and it's all set up.</dd>
      </dl>
    </div>
</div>

  <div class="arguments col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-6">
    <div class="argument-box card-2" style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'chalkboard.png', crop: :fill; %>') ;">
      <dl>
        <dt><h4 class="centered why-title">Unique algorithm to match your ideal job</h4></dt>
